value.string: Aston implemented a unit remodel for kitchen and bathrooms in order to maintain their AAA 3-diamond rating. Owner followed the remodel guidelines and remains in the Aston Rental Program. Kaanapali Shores boasts direct beach front location with western exposure offering year round sunset views. Enjoy the lush tropical landscaping and 2 fresh water swimming pools with hydro spa. Amenities include full health club, beach front restaurant and resort retail shops. Maintenance fees include All utilities. E.G. electric, (central A/C), water, sewer, trash, wi-fi access, cable TV, local phone service, storm, flood and general liability insurance. The maintenance fees also include a monthly contribution to the Capital Reserve Fund for major components to the building E.G. roofs, painting, pools, spas and other amenities. All this is paid for with 1 check per month.

Major Price Reduction! Recently upgraded with beautiful granite countertops and custom cabinetry in the kitchen and bathrooms, GE Profile kitchen appliances, tile flooring and artwork, this is a wonderful opportunity to own a 2 bedroom, 2 bath, 4th floor condominium with a direct oceanfront location at Kaanapali Shores. This beautiful resort is located on North Kaanapali Beach and offers many amenities for the active traveler with 2 pools, 3 lighted tennis courts, fitness and massage center, jet spas, complimentary scuba lessons, and wedding gazebo. An additional perk for parents and children is the resorts year-round Camp Kaanapali children's program. Other conveniences include an on-site salon, tropical flower shop, beach apparel store, and walking distance to nearby restaurants and shopping plaza.

Beautifully upgraded 2 bedroom, 2 full bath unit, located in the inner courtyard. Panoramic ocean and sunset views. Very tastefully decorated with all new kitchen and baths. New Frigidaire appliances. Master suite has its own reading porch and flat screen TV. Extra large locking owners closet. You can store all of your Maui necessities and travel with no luggage. This unit is in the Aston Hotels rental program. Rental details available upon request.

This is a "C" model floor plan that is the BEST for a 1-bedroom/1-bath apartment. This unit has had all the required Aston upgrades allowing it to be an "A" rated unit in the Aston vacation rental program. The unit is in an excellent location in the building with northern views of Molokai and the blue Pacific. Motivated Seller!

OCEAN VIEWS and all upgrades make this unit "one of the favorites"...Unit 513 was recently renovated and complies with Aston's rental program standards. Two pools, Jacuzzi and three tennis courts, fitness and massage facilities. Oceanfront restaurant, on-site salon, year round Camp Kaanapali for the kids, even a flower shop all on the famous Kaanapali makes this resort the place the world wants to own or visit. Great property for a 1031 exchange or just an investment. Come own your own little piece of paradise.

Great price for this ocean view 1 bedroom 1 bath unit at Kaanapali Shores. This unit offers privacy and a beautiful view of the island of Molokai. New kitchen and and bathroom remodel with granite counter tops and and all new cabinetry. Lots of on-site amenities for owners and guests with pools and tennis courts. Fitness room,salon and other shops and an on site restarurant and bar. At the north end of Kaanapali beach with swimming and surf right out in front.

YOUR beach front, 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom property is now available! Located on the 9th floor and renovated in 2010, the property at 904 is your perfect get-away for holidays in Paradise. Completed in 1980, this resorts has 463 units spread across 10.1 acres and offers a full array of resort amenities. Great location with many upgrades. New lower cabinets in the kitchen. New washer/dryer, refrigerator, stove and dishwasher. Granit counter tops in the kitchen and bath. Hardwood flooring. This unit is not in the front desk rental. Easy to show.

The kitchen has all new granite counter tops, cabinetry, self closing drawers, new fixtures, and appliances. Both bathrooms have new vanities with granite tops, fixtures and tub enclosures. Flat screen TVs in the living room and both bedrooms. Great rental income through the Aston pool. Rental figures are available upon request.
TOP FLOOR!- OCEAN VIEW! Awesome, Spectacular, Stupendous unit- See for yourself! Call today for a private showing! Electric is included in monthly maintenance fee.

This is an excellent opportunity to buy the much sought after large one bedroom floor plan at a great destination resort on Maui. This one bedroom unit is approximately 806 square feet. There is plenty of room to stretch out and relax. At this size it will comfortably sleep 4. The huge lanai is the perfect place to enjoy your morning coffee or an afternoon beverage. The unit is in original condition, so it is ready for you to add your creative touches to make it uniquely your own. If you are looking for a property with potential this is it. Kaanapali Shores is one of the best places on Maui to own a condo. The complex dominates the northernmost section of Mauis most famous Kaanapali Beach. It is a great walking beach. You can walk as much as a mile and a half to Black Rock. Kaanapali Shores is a destination condominium resort. It has everything you would expect at a resort. It has 2 swimming pools, hot tubs, an oceanfront restaurant, a fitness center, salon, ocean side massage, tennis courts, shops, barbeques and FREE internet for owners and guests.

This 2 bedroom 2 bath condo is inviting and open in the decor and feeling as soon as you walk into the living room and onto the lanai. The guest bedroom has a queen bed, closet and a large owners closet fo personal items to be stored while away. The master bedroom has a king bed and dual sinks fore more room. THe unit comes complete with a full size washer and dryer. The Kaanapali Shores complex has all the amenities a person could ask for.
